1
00:00:02,273 --> 00:00:09,573
RAYON IM Yisroel Pinksovitsh, KALETET SHNIYAH.

2
00:00:13,309 --> 00:00:18,905
az ir zent gekumen tsu Bukhnvald, ir hot bakumen a numer oyfn

3
00:00:18,152 --> 00:00:18,939
yo.

4
00:00:19,317 --> 00:00:22,888
oyfn CHUKTZAH, oyfn hemd, un

5
00:00:20,194 --> 00:00:22,230
oyf yo yo.

6
00:00:23,029 --> 00:00:24,542
vu zent ir gegangen?

7
00:00:24,717 --> 00:00:29,435
m'hot undz arayngefirt a blok, m'hot undz dortn arop geshtelt.

8
00:00:29,712 --> 00:00:34,616
dernokh dem dem andern tog hot der bruder zikh tsu mir aribergeshvertst

9
00:00:35,010 --> 00:00:37,265
un er iz gekumen tsu mir yedern tog.

10
00:00:37,626 --> 00:00:38,548
Avram?

11
00:00:37,660 --> 00:00:38,399
A-

12
00:00:38,399 --> 00:00:40,981
Avraham. dernokh dem iz er gekumen,

13
00:00:40,981 --> 00:00:46,634
hot er mir gezogt az im hot men fotografirt, un dort iz geven ven m'hot fotografirt,

14
00:00:46,634 --> 00:00:50,310
m'hot avekgefirt un m'hot fotografirt mitn,

15
00:00:50,502 --> 00:00:57,128
der numer iz geven oyfn hemd un m'hot opgefotografirt dos ponem, eyn mol in hitl un eyn onem hitl,

16
00:00:58,703 --> 00:01:03,270
az hot er zikh fun mir opgezegnt az m- im firt men avek.

17
00:01:03,478 --> 00:01:10,559
ober er hot zikh nisht geshtelt oyfn MASAIT, iz er tsurikgekumen, iz er gekumen er hot mir tsurik gezogt az er iz nisht avekgeforn,

18
00:01:11,275 --> 00:01:14,981
un in dem tog hot men mikh avekgefirt fotografirn,

19
00:01:15,780 --> 00:01:24,481
hob ikh im gezogt az mikh hot men shoyn fotografirt, dem andern tog hot men undz gefirt avek, iz er gekumen er hot mikh baleyt azoy fun der vaytns,

20
00:01:26,125 --> 00:01:43,466
er hot geveynt, undz hot men oyfgelodnt oyf a MASAIT, oyf aza gedektn MASAIT,

21
00:01:44,113 --> 00:01:46,756
un m'hot undz avekgefirt, ikh veys nisht vifl,

22
00:01:45,750 --> 00:01:49,491
ir zent geven tsuzamen mit Avram? neyn neyn.

23
00:01:47,877 --> 00:01:50,486
neyn, er iz geblibn dort in lager.

24
00:01:50,307 --> 00:01:50,993
yo.

25
00:01:51,049 --> 00:01:52,798
un mikh hot men avekgefirt.

26
00:01:53,175 --> 00:01:59,987
un m'hot undz avekgefirt, ikh veys nisht vifl tsayt mir ze'mir geforn, a por sho.

27
00:02:00,178 --> 00:02:07,091
ze'mir ongekumen in a filyal fun Bukhnvald Dora. a lager Dora.

28
00:02:07,519 --> 00:02:15,427
nisht a, D.O.R.A. arbayts-lager, oder?

29
00:02:13,375 --> 00:02:15,428
an arbayts-lager Dora.

30
00:02:16,108 --> 00:02:17,435
der arbayts-

31
00:02:16,159 --> 00:02:20,574
etlekhe sho a rayze fun fu- fun fun Bukhnvald.

32
00:02:20,007 --> 00:02:24,456
fun Bukhnvald ikh veys nisht vifl, tsi a sho, tsvey sho, ikh veys nisht vifl m'iz geforn.

33
00:02:25,356 --> 00:02:29,569
un dort, der lager iz gevezn azoy a bisl vi in a barg,

34
00:02:30,064 --> 00:02:35,390
ibern lager iz geven ongetsoygn aza nets tunkl grin mit LIGET grin,

35
00:02:35,700 --> 00:02:41,466
az m'zol nisht zen fun di luftn, dos iz gevezn gleyb ikh epes a sekretisher lager.

36
00:02:43,024 --> 00:02:45,330
dortn iz geven blokn.

37
00:02:46,652 --> 00:02:52,771
dem ershtn tog, undz ze'mir ongekumen nokh mitog, dos iz gevezn ober shvues ober erev shvues.

38
00:02:55,174 --> 00:03:05,006
hot men undz genumen un m'hot undz avekgefirt oyf a barg, un m'hot undz gegebn azolkhe, veyst ir, grobn, azoy vi m'grobt leym, azolkhe deys fun ayzn,

39
00:03:05,215 --> 00:03:10,474
hot men undz gegebn grobn, dos iz geven a shteyn, der shteyn iz geven a harter shteyn,

40
00:03:10,530 --> 00:03:13,595
er hot gehart a farb bloyer farb vi dem himl.

41
00:03:13,669 --> 00:03:16,312
un m'hot undz geheysn grobn dem shteyn.

42
00:03:16,588 --> 00:03:17,729
oysgrobn?

43
00:03:17,623 --> 00:03:25,883
grobn. dos hot men nisht gekont grobn, tsores oysteyln. m'hot undz geheysn grobn dem shteyn, dos hot geshpritst azolkhe shtikelekh funem shteyn,

44
00:03:25,883 --> 00:03:28,108
dos ponem iz gevezn blutik,

45
00:03:28,333 --> 00:03:33,930
un fun untn hobn di S.S. geshrign LASS! LASS! vu m'hot geharget un geshlogn.

46
00:03:34,425 --> 00:03:41,473
vi men hot dos geendikt, m'hot undz gebrengt arop hot men undz gezogt, az deys a matone oyf shvues.

47
00:03:42,458 --> 00:03:43,920
vos far a matone?

48
00:03:43,673 --> 00:03:46,485
nu m'hot m'hot geharget un geshlogn, m'hot undz geplogt.

49
00:03:48,769 --> 00:03:55,006
dernokh dem hob ikh dortn gearbet, dos iz ales geven in a tunel, untern tunel,

50
00:03:55,215 --> 00:04:02,397
m'hot gerisn alts tifer un unter dem tunel iz geven farshidene apteylungen, ikh gleyb s'hot gedarft zayn militerishe fabrikn.

51
00:04:03,417 --> 00:04:04,406
dort,

52
00:04:03,467 --> 00:04:04,895
tif in der erd?

53
00:04:04,750 --> 00:04:08,675
in untern barg. azoy in barg iz geven tuneln.

54
00:04:09,019 --> 00:04:13,485
m'hot gerisn di shteyn, un undz ho'mir gelodnt dem shteyn oyf azelkhe

55
00:04:14,031 --> 00:04:17,687
nu in vagondlekh kleyne, un gefirt aroys dem shteyn.

56
00:04:14,976 --> 00:04:16,084
vegelekh.

57
00:04:18,975 --> 00:04:25,823
ikh bin gevezn dortn oyf der arbet beerekh efsher a finef zeks vokhn.

58
00:04:25,823 --> 00:04:29,013
un dernokh dem hot men mikh shoyn nisht gebrengt

59
00:04:29,013 --> 00:04:34,648
tsurik fun der arbet oyf Dora, m'hot mikh avekgefirt oyf der anderer zayt tunel

60
00:04:34,648 --> 00:04:37,953
iz gevezn oykh an arbets-lager, Hartsungen.

61
00:04:37,943 --> 00:04:39,776
Hartsungl?

62
00:04:38,938 --> 00:04:40,484
Hartsungen.

63
00:04:42,448 --> 00:04:50,508
Hartsungen. H.A.R.Z.U.N.G.E.N.

64
00:04:51,527 --> 00:04:52,736
Hartsungen.

65
00:04:52,371 --> 00:04:56,111
dos iz geven in anderer zay- zayt fun Dora?

66
00:04:55,054 --> 00:04:56,839
fun dem tunel, yo.

67
00:04:56,839 --> 00:04:59,131
fun yener zayt dem barg. yo.

68
00:04:57,653 --> 00:04:59,098
fun yener zayt.

69
00:04:59,391 --> 00:05:03,064
dort hob ikh gearbet, s'hot geheysn a komando Urleger.

70
00:05:03,103 --> 00:05:11,518
undz ho'mir ge- gegrobn un nokh dem geshlepn nu karbirl, zeyer shvere karbirl,

71
00:05:11,625 --> 00:05:17,508
un az m'hot geshloy- getsoygn dem karbirl, azoy oyf yeder fir mentshn oyf der pleytse hot genumen karbirl, m'hot gefirt

72
00:05:17,937 --> 00:05:25,237
s'rayst az s'geven karbirlen azolkhe azolkhe groyse un dike karbirl, vegn CHASHMAL.

73
00:05:25,395 --> 00:05:27,363
ho'mir gearbet di gantse arbet.

74
00:05:28,197 --> 00:05:34,265
un dernokh dem, ikh veys nisht in velkhn khoydesh, hot men mikh ibergefirt in a lager Erlikh.

75
00:05:34,153 --> 00:05:35,581
Erlikh.

76
00:05:34,660 --> 00:05:35,801
Erlikh.

77
00:05:37,107 --> 00:05:40,594
keyn Hertsungen iz men gegangen tsu fus, a finef ze-

78
00:05:39,638 --> 00:05:40,579
eyn moment.

79
00:05:40,579 --> 00:05:46,179
E.R.L.I.C.H. vu ver iz vu i- vu iz dos geven?

80
00:05:45,696 --> 00:05:47,124
ikh vel aykh bald zogn.

81
00:05:47,367 --> 00:05:56,018
keyn Hartsungen ze'mir gegangen fun der arbet tsu fus. s'geven a finef zeks kilometer yedern tog. un oyf Erlikh hot men undz gefirt mit a tsug

82
00:05:56,378 --> 00:05:59,122
ober m'hot undz gebrengt oyf der zelber arbet.

83
00:05:59,128 --> 00:06:04,977
di zelbe arbet ho'mir gearbet, nor di in lager oyf bay nakht hot men undz gefirt keyn Erlikh.

84
00:06:09,118 --> 00:06:10,377
in yener,

85
00:06:10,271 --> 00:06:15,356
Erlikh iz geven a a arbayts-lager o- oder a vu m'hot geshloft?

86
00:06:12,561 --> 00:06:16,177
oykhet an arbay- a a filyal a lo- nu.

87
00:06:16,177 --> 00:06:21,381
di ales iz gevezn, di arbet iz geven dort bay di tuneln, nor geshlofn hot men gefirt keyn

88
00:06:21,522 --> 00:06:28,434
Dora, keyn Ha- Hartsungen un keyn Erlikh. nor Erlikh hot men gefirt, dos iz geven vayt, hot men gefirt mitn tsug.

89
00:06:29,773 --> 00:06:34,453
in yener finef un nayntsiker yor,

90
00:06:34,453 --> 00:06:37,935
ze'mir gekumen fun der arbet mir, ho'mir z-

91
00:06:36,979 --> 00:06:40,702
finef un nayntsik? finef un fertsiker yor.

92
00:06:38,329 --> 00:06:41,296
in finef un fertsiker yor finef un fertsiker yor.

93
00:06:41,296 --> 00:06:45,141
ze'mir gekumen fun der arbet, undz ho'mir di gantse tsayt

94
00:06:45,636 --> 00:06:49,123
keyn mol keyn CHOFESH nisht gehat, m'hot zikh keyn mol nisht gebodn,

95
00:06:49,433 --> 00:06:57,521
m'hot gegebn eyn mol in tog hot men gegebn ale tsu esn. oyf der nakht ven m'iz gekumen fun der arbet hot men gegebn a halbn liter MARAK un a shtikele broyt.

96
00:06:57,521 --> 00:06:59,636
deys iz gevezn di gantse esn.

97
00:06:59,355 --> 00:07:01,306
vi lang a tsayt zent ir?

98
00:07:01,583 --> 00:07:02,927
kimat a yor.

99
00:07:01,600 --> 00:07:04,311
kimat a yor.

100
00:07:03,372 --> 00:07:04,733
in dem, yo.

101
00:07:05,532 --> 00:07:11,938
m'iz geven zeyer shoyn opgeshvakht, un antshuldikts, m'hot kinim a sakh gehat.

102
00:07:11,978 --> 00:07:14,503
fun shvakhekeytn, m'hot zikh nisht gezoybert.

103
00:07:14,543 --> 00:07:17,102
ot mir ze'mir gekumen oyf Erlikhn lager,

104
00:07:15,842 --> 00:07:19,566
zey laysn un s'tut vey? tseblutit?

105
00:07:22,710 --> 00:07:24,577
ir veyst vos kinim heyst?

106
00:07:23,554 --> 00:07:24,645
yo yo.

107
00:07:25,073 --> 00:07:32,424
iz men gekumen, m'hot geheysn far yedern oystun di zakhn un tsambindn di zakhn in aza pekele, un oyvn zol blaybn di numer,

108
00:07:32,852 --> 00:07:35,175
un m'hot genumen oyskokhn di zakhn.

109
00:07:36,750 --> 00:07:44,742
bay nakht hot men gebrengt di zakhn, m'hot gezogt yeder zol vartn, m'vet rufn yedern's numer un yeder's vet zikh kumen mit dem numer tsunemen in blok.

110
00:07:45,677 --> 00:07:47,341
ir hot aleyn gevasht?

111
00:07:46,977 --> 00:07:50,498
NO, m'hot dos genumen un m'hot dos m'hot dem

112
00:07:48,782 --> 00:07:53,940
vayl di kleyder UNK, ober di UNK oyfn oyfn,

113
00:07:52,714 --> 00:07:57,280
m'hot nisht gevasht gornisht. gornisht hot men nisht gevashn.

114
00:07:59,667 --> 00:08:06,276
m'hot ongehoybn tsu rufn, ikh hob gevart un gevart, m'hot nisht gerufn. nokh dem, s'shoyn ales tsegangen, ikh bin shoyn geven zeyer shvakh,

115
00:08:07,007 --> 00:08:12,451
bin ikh avek ikh hob getrofn dortn kleyder, ikh hob ongetun di kleyder, s'nisht mayn numer,

116
00:08:13,791 --> 00:08:22,762
s'iz di kni iz im naket, ales tserisn di kleyder in gantsn, yeder iz tseklapt. un ikh hob ongehoybn tsu veynen, vi zol ikh geyn? un m'shrayt shoyn, "geyn aroys oyf der arbet!"

117
00:08:24,912 --> 00:08:31,641
ikh bin aroysgega- arayngegangen in di SHIRUTIM iz dort geven azoy vu dort iz geven rusishe gefangene,

118
00:08:31,641 --> 00:08:38,641
zey hobn gehat azelkhe tserisene kleyder, zey hobn avekgevorfn in der kanalizatsye, in BIYUV, un ikh hob mayn oykhet aropgevorfn in BIYUV.

119
00:08:38,817 --> 00:08:40,414
ikh hob mir gerekhnt azoy.

120
00:08:40,808 --> 00:08:45,779
shtarbn vel ikh nisht oyshaltn oyf der arbet naketerheyt, un ikh vel do vet men mikh hargenen.

121
00:08:45,786 --> 00:08:47,518
dos ales. ikh hob aropgevorfn.

122
00:08:47,727 --> 00:08:53,222
azoy ale zenen avek un undz ze'mir geblibn fuftsn mentshn naket. in gantsn naket.

123
00:08:52,485 --> 00:08:53,947
shikh yo,?

124
00:08:53,852 --> 00:08:56,563
naket, azoy vi di mame hot geborn.

125
00:08:55,759 --> 00:08:57,086
naket un borves.

126
00:08:56,974 --> 00:08:57,643
yo.

127
00:08:58,982 --> 00:09:06,131
ze'mir gevezn yener, feber, un beerekh halb merts naket.

128
00:09:06,930 --> 00:09:11,007
m'hot undz gegebn esn hot men gegebn nor a halb fun dem vos m'hot gegebn far andere.

129
00:09:12,297 --> 00:09:14,569
shoyn a, un mir ho'mir naketerheyt

130
00:09:14,929 --> 00:09:19,372
ho'mir gearbet in lager, azelkhe arbets-lagern, m'iz fleg aroysgeyn naket,

131
00:09:19,372 --> 00:09:22,888
azoy vi di mame hot gehat, azoy iz men umgegangen in droysn naket.

132
00:09:24,244 --> 00:09:29,756
ikh hob fargesn tsu zogn, un ven mir ze'mir gekumen di ershte nakht in Dora, ikh hob gehat mayne shikh,

133
00:09:30,387 --> 00:09:38,059
hot men geheysn oystun di shikh un azoy geyn shlofn. undz ze'mir arayngekumen in blok. tsu fri iz men gekumen un keyn shikh shoyn nisht gevezn.

134
00:09:38,335 --> 00:09:41,737
hob ikh bakumen a por shikh, dos iz geven fun holts,

135
00:09:42,823 --> 00:09:48,133
s'nor geven aza lekhl dem fus arayntsushtupn in dem holts, un in dem iz men gegangen.

136
00:09:50,383 --> 00:09:53,549
un azoy bin ikh gevezn naket.

137
00:09:54,518 --> 00:09:57,920
m'iz shoyn gevezn in gantsn opgeshvakht, m'hot shoyn gornisht nisht geton,

138
00:09:56,847 --> 00:09:59,355
vi lang zent ir geven naket un borves?

139
00:09:58,990 --> 00:10:00,536
karge dray khadoshim.

140
00:10:00,728 --> 00:10:02,561
karge dray khadoshim?!

141
00:10:01,740 --> 00:10:02,505
yo.

142
00:10:02,505 --> 00:10:04,232
s'nisht geven keyn kley-

143
00:10:02,989 --> 00:10:05,328
s'merts, april, s'iz,

144
00:10:05,655 --> 00:10:10,846
nisht april, s'gevezn yener, feber un halb merts, s'beerekh.

145
00:10:11,848 --> 00:10:18,080
a mol iz gekumen ver s'lebn mir geshlofn, nisht keyn yid, a fun Poyln iz er gevezn.

146
00:10:18,080 --> 00:10:24,077
zogt er far mir azoy, dir iz gut, zogt er, du geyst nisht azoy shver arbetn.

147
00:10:24,319 --> 00:10:29,049
zog ikh far im, ikh volt gegangen gern arbetn, nor ikh zol hobn kleyder.

148
00:10:29,049 --> 00:10:34,050
zogt er, kum tsum lager's ELTESTER, zogt er, ikh gib dir mayne kleyder. zog ikh, geyt!

149
00:10:34,562 --> 00:10:38,116
bin ikh avek, er hot mir gegebn zayne kleyder,

150
00:10:38,325 --> 00:10:42,487
m'hot mir gegebn a shtikl aza fets un ikh hob ongeshribn mayn numer,

151
00:10:42,510 --> 00:10:46,689
un ikh hob mir tsugeneyt, un azoy bin ikh avek oyf der arbet,

152
00:10:47,708 --> 00:10:53,220
mer hob ikh mikh keyn Erlikh nisht umgekert. vi mir ze'mir demolts aroys, mer hob ikh mikh nisht umgekert.

153
00:10:53,428 --> 00:10:55,936
ze'mir tsurikgekumen oyf Hartsungen.

154
00:10:55,673 --> 00:10:56,882
Hartsungen?

155
00:10:56,719 --> 00:10:57,556
yo.

156
00:10:58,356 --> 00:11:06,956
in Hartsungen ze'mir gevezn, dos iz gevezn, ikh veys nisht BEDIYUK vos a datum s'iz gevezn,

157
00:11:06,996 --> 00:11:10,145
s'geven tsvishn ferdn un tsvishn nayntn april.

158
00:11:11,147 --> 00:11:16,996
undz ho'mir nisht gevust far gornisht. nor s'shoyn geven m'hot shoyn nisht gekont arbetn. m'hot tsen minut gearbet oyf der arbet,

159
00:11:18,066 --> 00:11:22,363
un dos iberike, far di amerikaner hobn shtark bombardirt.

160
00:11:18,996 --> 00:11:19,696
far vos?

161
00:11:23,112 --> 00:11:30,969
flegn blozn di S.S., m'hot bombardirt un m'fleg arayn in tunel, undz ho'mir zikh gefreyt az m'hot bombardirt, az m'darf nisht arbetn.

162
00:11:31,313 --> 00:11:33,096
m'iz shoyn geven zeyer shvakh,

163
00:11:33,827 --> 00:11:39,524
di letste nakht hot men undz shoyn gebrengt nor bay nakht in lager, in der halber nakht.

164
00:11:40,071 --> 00:11:44,739
un mir ze'mir tsu fri, az m'vekt undz nisht tsu geyn oyf der arbet.

165
00:11:45,960 --> 00:11:52,957
m'vekt nisht. a mol iz men gekumen, m'shrayt oyf apel m'zol geyn. apel iz yedes aroysgegangen, yo yo.

166
00:11:50,331 --> 00:11:52,367
apel, yo, m'tseylt.

167
00:11:53,419 --> 00:11:57,395
m'iz aroys oyf apel, hot men gezogt az yeder vet krign a broyt,

168
00:11:58,144 --> 00:12:04,230
un zikh mitnemen ales, di shisl. m'hot gehat aza blekhn shisele a royt tsu esn,

169
00:12:05,468 --> 00:12:07,672
un m'firt undz in an andern lager.

170
00:12:09,315 --> 00:12:13,781
ober oyf dos ende hot men nisht gegebn keyn broyt, m'hot nor gegebn a shtikele broyt,

171
00:12:13,939 --> 00:12:17,240
keyn esn hot men shoyn nisht gegebn, vayl zet men s'shoyn nisht geven tsayt,

172
00:12:17,449 --> 00:12:23,113
un m'hot undz gefirt aroys oysern lager, un m'iz gegangen tsu fus, toyznt a sakh toyznter mentshn.

173
00:12:20,706 --> 00:12:21,577
tsu fus?

174
00:12:23,997 --> 00:12:27,567
iz men gegangen tog un bay nakht.

175
00:12:27,658 --> 00:12:29,390
etlekhe vokhn iz men gegangen.

176
00:12:29,447 --> 00:12:30,774
tog un bay nakht?

177
00:12:30,308 --> 00:12:31,123
yo.

178
00:12:31,123 --> 00:12:36,124
di daytshn flegn zikh shteln opruen zikh, vegn zikh hobn zey undz oykh gelozt opruen.

179
00:12:37,345 --> 00:12:42,384
